  "title": "C-22 Adhesive Remover Solvent Spray",
  "body_html": "<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Lux Hair' C-22 Hair Solvent has been developed to remove adhesive residues quickly and effectively from hair systems and the scalp. It is an effective solvent for all kind of adhesives and tapes.</span><br></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Advantages</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"3\" data-mce-src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fast-acting hair solvent for removing adhesive residues.</li>\n<li>Less aggressive than other solvents on the market.</li>\n<li>Contains moisturizing active ingredients.</li>\n<li>Specific formulation for cleaning hair prostheses, wigs, and extensions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Active Ingredients</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"3\" data-mce-src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\"></p>\n<p>With lanolin, citrus oils, and other organic moisturizing agents.</p>\n<p>\u00a0<br></p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Recommendations for use</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"3\" data-mce-src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Spray C22 and leave on for a maximum of 1 minute while massaging the scalp to remove persistent glue residues.</li>\n<li>After cleaning, wash the piece with shampoo and brush it.</li>\n<li>Finally, rinse with plenty of water.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle et_pb_module et_pb_accordion_item et_pb_accordion_item_2  et_pb_toggle_close\">\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\"><br></h5>\n</div>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle et_pb_module et_pb_accordion_item et_pb_accordion_item_3 et_clickable et_pb_toggle_open\">\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Product safety data sheet</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://luxhair.es/en/Product/luxhair-c22-solvent#:~:text=safety%20data%20sheet-,Link,-Related%20products\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Link</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<ul></ul>",
